messages.title: A message from Cat Smith
messages.content: I am sorry that we missed you on our recent visit. It has been an honour to serve as your Labour MP since 2015 and I hope to have your support once again.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Cat has stood up for our local health services in Parliament and locally. She has vowed to always vote against privatisation.
Cat has been instrumental in getting flood defences built, stopping fracking and securing better transport services.
She also secured a Climate Emergency declaration by Parliament and is pushing the government to go further in cutting harmful emissions.
